                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;16:28:54&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; John Hammond: Di, Why do you pass the FID rather than the object when calling mdd_migrate() from mdt_reint_migrate_internal()? Doing it your way opens you up to hangs in lu_object_find_at().&lt;br/&gt;
